      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it still has that brand-new feel. It drives like a dream and looks absolutely stunning. I'm really sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
