    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector's standards. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a factory-fresh exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. The interior is equally flawless, featuring premium leather that remains supple and matte, free from any wear or creasing, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized dealerships; a complete binder of service records is included. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its low-mileage, fair-weather-only history. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key masterpiece that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 44500.0,
